<h1 id='about-turtlecoin'>About TurtleCoin</h1>
<p>TurtleCoin is a fast, easy and private cryptocurrency which allows you to send money to friends and businesses.</p>

<p>One of TurtleCoin&#39;s main goals is to make things as simple and as accessible as possible for everyday people, creating a cryptocurrency which is inviting, fun and friendly.</p>

<p>TurtleCoin&#39;s code is forked from the Bytecoin code, and it has majorly the same privacy features you&#39;ll find in Monero and Aeon. Every transaction is private unless you choose to make it public.</p>

<p>Some of the main features of TurtleCoin include:</p>

<ul>
<li>On-chain privacy</li>
<li>Only two decimal places</li>
<li>Fast transactions</li>
<li>User-centric developers</li>
<li>Easy to mine </li>
<li>Easy to use</li>
<li>Amazing community</li>
</ul>

